about transforming,

00:37:16.090 --> 00:37:17.610
it creates longing.

00:37:17.610 --> 00:37:20.660
If people are trying to
change and get somewhere,

00:37:20.660 --> 00:37:21.840
the journey is hard.

00:37:21.840 --> 00:37:23.730
And it's story that's
the coping mechanism.

00:37:23.730 --> 00:37:25.650
It's story that
helps them recommit.

00:37:25.650 --> 00:37:27.480
It's story that makes
