to start by empathetically

00:43:14.220 --> 00:43:15.450
understanding their audience.

00:43:15.450 --> 00:43:16.140
Who are they?

00:43:16.140 --> 00:43:17.490
What are they feeling?

00:43:17.490 --> 00:43:19.290
What are they thinking?

00:43:19.290 --> 00:43:20.710
